          "No voy nunca. (I never go.)",
          "No tengo nada. (I don't have nothing)",
          "No viene nadie. (Nobody is coming.)",
          "",
          "You can also front-load them:",
          "Nada tengo. Nadie viene. Nunca voy.",
          "But the double negative is more common."
